title: Quartz Countertops Included in This 1BR/1BA Apartment Ready for Lease
posting_body: ['Welcome to The Colonnade Apartments!', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', '$2,605 - $2,908', '.', '1 Bed 1 Bath .', '700 Sq.Ft', '* Unit 413 - Available Now', '* Unit 624 - Available', 'Now', '* Unit 601 - Available', 'Now', '* Unit 701 - Available Now', '* Unit 506 - Available', 'Now', 'The Colonnade Apartments', 'Address:', '201 S 4th Street San Jose, CA 95112', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Tour this one-bedroom, one-bathroom floor plan from The Colonnade Apartments!', 'Features in this home include high ceilings, double-pane windows, and multi-panel inner doors.', 'The kitchen has all-electric stainless steel appliances, cabinets with brushed nickel hardware, and quartz countertops.', 'Large closets and in-wall USB charging ports make apartment living more convenient.', 'While this model has a private patio or balcony, the resort-like apartment lifestyle extends outside the home with the sparkling pool and a soothing sauna.', 'The Colonnade Apartments additionally provides access to a state-of-the-art fitness center, a clubhouse, and a business center.', 'Just beyond the community, downtown San Jose, SJSU, and Interstate 280 are all just minutes away, making it easy to enjoy the area close to hope or commute all around the Bay.', 'Schedule your tour of the community today to see The Colonnade for yourself!', 'FLOORPLAN/UNIT\u2002 \u2002FEATURES', 'Mountain view', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Monday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Sunday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
